## Startup sequence (`cmd/server/main.go`)

1. Load `.env` via godotenv (no-op if absent â€” dev convenience only)
2. Parse all config from env vars â†’ `internal/config.Config`
3. Set the default `slog` logger (format/level from config)
4. Connect pgxpool with retry â†’ `internal/db.Connect`
5. Initialize S3 storage client â†’ `internal/storage.New`
6. Start River background job processor â†’ `internal/worker.Start`
7. Choose JWT validator: HMACValidator (HS256) using `JWT_SECRET`
8. Build chi router with all middleware and routes â†’ `internal/router.New`
9. Start HTTP server; block on SIGINT/SIGTERM; graceful shutdown

